{"tid":526266,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"馬雲唔用支付寶有幾奇？比特幣大會都拒絕比特幣購票啦 (17:41)","createTime":"2018-01-11T13:03:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-11T13:48:08.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d57002c5b07e5a29234001a83ce9e797dc1d99bd","tid":526266,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20180111/img/20180111174145fi_p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20180111%2Fimg%2F20180111174145fi_p1.jpg&h=9e017e5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=hnFfUxQz5t0uSK50yrR20IM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=55d63241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】是咁的，報道指馬雲夜蒲酒吧，找數時竟用銀行卡而非自家旗下的支付寶，網民當然圍觀「食花生」，不過此等「身體卻很誠實」行為，又何是馬雲獨有。<br />\n<br />\n外電報道，比特幣大會下周將在美國邁阿密舉行，大會宣布叫停接受比特幣購票。大會在其網站上公告稱，由於網絡擁堵和人工處理速度緩慢，已決定停止接受最後一分鐘的比特幣付款購買門票。事件無疑突顯了目前比特幣交易的缺點：速度慢，成本高，勞動密集。<br />\n<br />\n大會的組織者Moe Levin表示，他的公司正努力將比特幣現金或其他費用較低的數字資產整合進票務系統。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20180111/20180111174145fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20180111%2F20180111174145fi.html&d=hnFfUxQz5t0uSK50yrR20IM9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=5ca6e925\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20180111/20180111174145fi.html</a>"},{"pid":"beb4f4ccf7ae1b63df0d13d519a38c0e31ec85ba","tid":526266,"uid":63670,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:05:36.000Z","msg":"怕幫手機公司賣廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"c60de9af361f9bb0fa743b633b0a026a93916c64","tid":526266,"uid":5278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:12:35.000Z","msg":"用bitcoin做payment根本垃圾黎"},{"pid":"ed6d394e62d6f313f997159f99e0011ebbd1d5e6","tid":526266,"uid":34010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T13:45:52.000Z","msg"